packages/d2mini/README.md
     1→# D2Mini is a minimal IVM implementation based on Differential Dataflow
     3→D2Mini is a minimal implementation of the D2TS dataflow graph library but simplified and without the complexities of multi-dimensional versioning.
     4→
     5→The API is almost identical to D2TS, but without the need to specify a version when sending data, or to send a frontier to mark the end of a version.
     6→
     7→### Basic Usage

